{"tid":1620032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略＆心態］蒙面法唯一應對方案，請廣傳","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:53:21.000Z","uid":179648,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"205d0d29863cf8dadf646a6e1d03e4776fd8d124","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"蒙面法宇宙唯一應對方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">救人！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>打狗，救人！</strong></span></span><br />\n要有決心救手足，一個都唔可以被捕！<br />\n<br />\n話蒙面法係笑話，只係為其他緊急法鋪路嘅，我話你知，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">蒙面法本身就係目的</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目的係慳返查cctv搜屋搜證</span></strong></span>，唔洗用資源入你非法集結，一個面罩，48小時內即告即坐一年<br />\n<br />\n1. 狗同律政司喺每次拘捕都要大量人手搜證，跟踪、搜屋、查cctv，非法集結同暴動都要法官信納先入到。<br />\n<br />\n蒙面法唔撚洗，拉你個刻有蒙面就係有，即刻齊證據，上庭，即判，同掉垃圾即罰1500蚊一樣。變相慳咗數以千計人手查案。<br />\n<br />\n2. 48小時內已經可以上庭，因為告蒙面法唔洗48小時已經齊證據！即告，即坐，想見律師，保釋？已經唔洗。<br />\n<br />\n3. 加速判刑，阻嚇力升n倍。而家拉嘅人本身要幾年先判刑，而家係一拉即判，蒙面法無空間比法官減刑。運動未完已經有人入監獄，對運動嘅所有人心理壓力極大。<br />\n<br />\n而上分析絕無誇大。67暴動期間嘅緊急法，令曾鈺成弟弟曾德成因為派傳單，即拉即判兩年監。<br />\n<br />\n所以，蒙面法唔係比你走精面，咩化妝阿拉只會更多人站出來，錯！拉唔到你就係，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">所有拉到嘅人，48小時內就可以判1年監啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">救人！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>打狗，救人！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c13e1e8d0dd5888ef0539ce7f604f8f2d7c4fc69","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:18:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"527bc2fcaa1b9aa4171d543329c220fd06a53557","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12f8bd051052b2fa5310ad508948b9f819f62a96","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"［戰略＆心態］蒙面法唯一應對方案，請廣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1620032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1620032</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3746db52594d540a4f99801952d425224d1fe45e","tid":1620032,"uid":324569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:20:40.000Z","msg":"1. 成立警衛公司，承接集會遊行期間真正保護市民工作，完全正當合理蒙面，「為人身安全而蒙面」<br />\n2. 逐步取代警隊<br />\n集思廣益！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191004/large/1570176804_03ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191004%2Flarge%2F1570176804_03ca.png&h=b11d167a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"925d40081fddb299751bd6c0abd198da2c4f4679","tid":1620032,"uid":170445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c63ff3d052b8726daa992e5ccb33282b8734d8ee","tid":1620032,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"香港人，反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119bb01bbfdf9da48e64e7f7c5cccaa62f9332a1","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dda5959a166f09a46b8b0cb1d4e6bbe25673399","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27b2a6ecd09c80dd495ce35fe7206cb277f509a9","tid":1620032,"uid":155493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05dff168084606e60321ed3888f0ca52a99d9118","tid":1620032,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf0810225a70a